{"type":"message","id":"e1c63221","parentId":"a0031255","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:17:15.578Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's 4:17 AM on Saturday, April 4th, 2026. This is within the \"quiet hours\" of 23:00-08:00 mentioned in HEARTBEAT.md. \n\nAccording to HEARTBEAT.md:\n- Core Rules say: 晚上 23:00-08:00 非紧急情况保持安静；安静不等于停工，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务\n- I should check if there are active tasks, workspace backup, quant ops, or self-improvement tasks to run\n\nLet me check the HEARTBEAT.md which is already in context. It mentions:\n1. Workspace backup - daily, via checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md\n\n\n2. Quant ops - daily heartbeat execution, with pre-market checks happening on trading days between 09:20-09:40\n3. Self-improvement - once daily in the afternoon or evening\n\nSince it's 4:17 AM on a Saturday, I'm outside the quiet hours window and today isn't a trading day, so quant ops pre-market checks won't run. I should verify whether there's an active task in the system that needs attention before proceeding with the standard heartbeat checks.","thinkingSignature":"85d97ea7bf482624cb50a8a36dc8c1454343077286e8e6f2df48c9fca081102f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fe6dcr3ogx08_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fe6dcr3ogx08_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ 2>/dev/null && cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md 2>/dev/null || echo \"NO_FILE\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":353,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":25967,"totalTokens":26394,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775247428201,"responseId":"061f5344747e86c8be4fb1eb350c64d4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dbb80281","parentId":"e1c63221","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:17:15.662Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_fe6dcr3ogx08_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: done\nPriority: P1\nStarted: 2026-04-03 21:10\nUpdated: 2026-04-03 21:12\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/daily_stock_analysis\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲确认执行 daily_stock_analysis 上游 4 个新 commit 合并\nResume Entry: 先备份当前分支，再执行 upstream/main 合并，重点解决 src/search_service.py 冲突（上游 announcements+资金流 + 本地 throttle 冷却逻辑）\n\n## Goal\n- 将 upstream/main 的 4 个新 commit 合入，保留本地 THS bridge 与 throttle 逻辑，并纳入 upstream 的公司公告/资金流搜索功能\n\n## Acceptance\n- 完成 merge commit 并解决全部冲突\n- 同时保留：本地 throttle 冷却机制 + upstream 新增 announcements 维度 + 主力资金流工具\n- 语法验证通过\n\n## Current\n- 已完成全部验证，结果汇总\n\n## Next\n- 解 src/search_service.py 冲突（throttle 逻辑 + announcements 维度 + 资金流）\n- 运行语法验证并汇总结果\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-03 21:10] 已完成评估：4 个 upstream commit 均建议合入，其中 #2(search_service 冲突)需要同时保留本地 throttle 和上游新功能\n\n## Evidence\n- 4 个新 upstream commits: 17776b4(bot异常日志) / 709604f(公告+资金流) / 5ba37c4(WebUI) / dffa29c(测试时区)\n- 当前 HEAD: 7ebf0fd\n- 分支跟踪已修正到 upstream/main\n- Merge 收口 commit: 67d7eb3 Merge remote-tracking branch upstream/main\n- 4 个 upstream commits 全部合入: 17776b4 / 709604f / 5ba37c4 / dffa29c\n- _key_disabled_until throttle 逻辑保留: grep 6 次\n- announcements 维度新增: grep 3 次\n- capital_flow 数据工具已合入: 9 次引用\n- 语法验证: python3 -m py_compile 无报错\n\n## Blockers\n- None\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775247435650}}
