{"type":"message","id":"57a3af50","parentId":"5c141985","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:23:07.036Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qlsh3ayve3jh_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Self-Improvement Daily Report - 2026-04-04\n\n- 生成时间: 2026-04-04 16:22:56\n- 学习条目: 41\n- 错误条目: 33\n- 需求条目: 1\n- 待关注高优先级: 32\n- 可自动提升条目: 0\n\n## 状态分布\n- pending: 69\n- promoted: 3\n- resolved: 3\n\n## 优先级分布\n- critical: 2\n- high: 33\n- low: 13\n- medium: 27\n\n## Area 分布\n- backend: 18\n- config: 14\n- docs: 25\n- holdings: 1\n- infra: 12\n- research: 1\n- tests: 4\n\n## 高优先级待处理\n- LRN-20260308-002 | high | pending | 用户指出“多账户持仓抓取不准”，核心问题是把“账本缓存可读”误当作“账户切换已生效”，导致连续三轮结果一致却未在第一时间明确说明采集口径受限。\n- LRN-20260315-006 | high | pending | For future XTP integration, isolate all XTP SDK calls in a subprocess; never call InsertOrder directly from the main Python process due to callback deadlock risk\n- LRN-20260315-007 | high | pending | Do not mix XTP trading market enums with quote exchange enums; they are reversed between Shanghai and Shenzhen\n- LRN-20260315-008 | high | pending | Outside trading hours, XTP paper trading may reject limit orders because quotes are unavailable; scheduling must gate order placement to market hours\n- LRN-20260315-009 | high | pending | AKShare full-market A-share endpoint stock_zh_a_spot_em may fail outside mainland China; use single-stock queries or alternate data source fallback\n- LRN-20260315-010 | high | pending | Do not let AI generate stock picks or reports without an explicit data-backed decision path; ban vague 'common sense' justification\n- LRN-20260315-011 | high | pending | Preferred quant research system architecture: OpenClaw orchestration + multi-search MCP layer + layered market data + XTP subprocess isolation + cron-based monitoring windows\n- LRN-20260315-012 | high | pending | Do not restate external quant architecture as-is; adapt the system description to Zhang Ling's actual data stack, which includes Tushare and Yahoo Finance\n- LRN-20260315-013 | high | pending | When corrected on prior statements, revisit the workspace evidence before summarizing architecture; do not overwrite yesterday's documented data-source policy with a generic external template\n- LRN-20260315-014 | high | pending | When asked to learn from external examples, extract strengths and adapt them to the existing system instead of copying the architecture wholesale\n- LRN-20260315-015 | high | pending | Do not ask Zhang Ling whether to continue for procedural optimization work; continue automatically and interrupt only for important decisions\n- LRN-20260316-001 | high | pending | Asynchronous promises to continue work later must be converted into a verifiable execution chain in the same turn\n- LRN-20260316-002 | high | pending | Do not claim 'I’ll continue pushing app optimization myself' without verifiable follow-through in the stated time window\n- LRN-20260316-004 | high | pending | Do not promise '中午前修复' without device-level validation; report missed deadline directly\n- LRN-20260316-005 | high | pending | After user says 'programmatic tasks don't ask me', proactively report new artifacts without waiting to be asked\n- LRN-20260316-007 | high | pending | 在“来福投研会”群聊中必须以投研组织语境发言，不能把主会话的英语学习产品职责直接套用到该群\n- LRN-20260316-008 | high | pending | For mobile compatibility bugs, stop patching a broken vendor system path after one confirmatory retest; pivot earlier to an alternative owned path and verify required assets upfront\n- LRN-20260317-002 | high | pending | 用户明确要求所有面向她展示的内容都应是中文，不能再出现英文卡片或英文面板文案\n- LRN-20260319-001 | high | pending | 做出买入推荐时必须先接入当日盘中大盘与个股实时状态，不能事后再修正名单\n- LRN-20260324-001 | high | pending | 量化持仓分析不能仅按亏损幅度直接给出减仓/清仓倾向，必须先按中低频持有逻辑评估趋势、行业位置、个股发展趋势与持仓角色。\n\n## 可自动提升候选\n- 无\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775290987027}}
